---
/**
 * /en/privacy/ — Privacy Policy (English).
 */
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy · NilaTales"
  description="Privacy policy for NilaTales — how we handle your data."
  locale="en"
>
  <article class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-rounded font-bold text-kohl-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-kohl-700 leading-relaxed">
      <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> June 2026</p>

      <p>
        NilaTales (nilatales.com) is a static website for children's stories. We are
        committed to protecting your privacy, especially since our audience includes
        children.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-rounded font-bold text-lg text-kohl-700 mt-6">What we collect</h2>
      <p>
        NilaTales is a static site — we do not run a server-side database. We do not
        collect personal information from visitors. The newsletter signup form uses
        a third-party provider (Formspree) and only collects the email address you
        voluntarily submit.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-rounded font-bold text-lg text-kohl-700 mt-6">Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        We do not use cookies for tracking. The bedtime mode preference is stored in
        your browser's localStorage, which stays on your device and is never sent to us.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-rounded font-bold text-lg text-kohl-700 mt-6">Third-party services</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
        <li>Google Fonts — for typography (loads font files from Google's CDN)</li>
        <li>YouTube — embedded videos (only loaded when you click play)</li>
        <li>Formspree — newsletter signup form processing</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-rounded font-bold text-lg text-kohl-700 mt-6">Children's privacy</h2>
      <p>
        NilaTales is designed for children. We do not knowingly collect personal
        information from children. The newsletter signup is intended for parents
        and guardians, not children themselves.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-rounded font-bold text-lg text-kohl-700 mt-6">Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about privacy? Reach out via our
        <a href="https://github.com/nivinlabs/nilatales" class="text-twilight-500 hover:text-twilight-700 underline">GitHub repo</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>